Step-2 Create De-normalized Tables and Load them using the Data file. 2
  • Run the Provided Data file into SQL Server Management Studio to create and load de-normalized data into those tables.

                        

  • Afrer you run the data file script, Refresh the Database. Right Click ColaberryResortrealty Database--> Refreseh               
  • You will see the Tables have been created into the ColaberryResortRealtyDatabase.
  • Run the SELECT statement to see the Data into those Table. ( The Code file has been provided below)

Please follow the below link to see how to create Dimension  and Fact Tables:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=34pEmQm7SDc
